OL,3,CHospice bosses battle against rising
OL,4,Ccosts and drop in donations
OL,6,FCumbrian hospice bosses are calling
OL,7,Ffor changes to how the palliative care
OL,8,Fsector is funded, as it becomes
OL,9,F'harder and harder to operate'.
OL,11,FThe Eden Valley Hospice, based in
OL,12,FCarlisle, is mostly funded by
OL,13,Ffundraising and charitable gifts,
OL,14,Fwhich have significantly reduced.
OL,16,FIt comes as concerns grow for the
OL,17,Ffuture of the hospice as bosses battle
OL,18,Fagainst rising costs, decline in
OL,19,Fdonations and increased demand.
