OL,3,CHospice bosses battle against rising
OL,4,Ccosts and drop in donations
OL,6,FThe hospice is a charity dedicated to
OL,7,Fproviding specialist care for adults
OL,8,Fin north Cumbria who have life
OL,9,Flimiting conditions.
OL,11,FJulie Clayton, Eden Valley Hospice,
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are struggling with the cost
OL,13,Fof living. We've been affected by the
OL,14,Fcost of giving and we are probably not
OL,15,Fexpecting to bring in as much money
OL,16,Fthis year as it costs us to run. And
OL,17,Fwe're seeing that right across the
OL,18,Fhospice sector.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
