OL,3,CHospice bosses battle against rising
OL,4,Ccosts and drop in donations
OL,6,FShe continued: "There's a real need to
OL,7,Fhave a conversation about hospice
OL,8,Ffunding specifically and not everybody
OL,9,Fthat's dying will need to come to a
OL,10,Fhospice. But we know that we are
OL,11,Fcaring for patients who are much more
OL,12,Fcomplex.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
