OL,3,CHospice bosses battle against rising
OL,4,Ccosts and drop in donations
OL,6,F"We know that the public has been
OL,7,Fsubsidising that care through their
OL,8,Fgenerous donations for a long, long
OL,9,Ftime, and we need to have a real think
OL,10,Fabout whether it's okay for an NHS
OL,11,Fdoctor to be providing that care fully
OL,12,Fpaid for by the NHS. But a hospice
OL,13,Fdoctor to be paid for by parachute
OL,14,Fjumps."
OL,16,FChanges to minimum wage and national
OL,17,Finsurance in the UK Governments
OL,18,FOctober budget have also increased
OL,19,Foutgoings by #300,000 for the Hospice.
